item.title: An unfeeling mouth
item.description: I can´t feel most of my mouth. My tongue can move but can´t taste or feel touch. My bottom lip feels like my tongue sticking out of my mouth in a constant pout.

item.title: Insanity?
item.description: From May 2008 How intensely have you questioned your sanity? Today my brain perceived differently- I saw at angles I hadn’t seen before and heard at times I couldn’t explain.

item.title: It
item.description: From 2003: . . It suffered times when It almost drowned in the unruly sea, in wild tempests. The sharp, icy jagged teeth of Cruelty
